productReviews.reviewText: My neighbor Krista has one of these. She works as a salesman and she says it looks soapy.
I saw one of these in Saint Pierre and Miquelon and I bought one.
My co-worker Alek has one of these. He says it looks white.
I tried to belly-flop it but got Turkish Delight all over it.
The box this comes in is 4 meter by 5 foot and weights 18 kilogram.
